<a href="/questions/1422945-i-m-only-a-little-over-100-pages-into-this">I&#39;m only a little over 100 pages into this book and it&#39;s excruciatingly painful to read. If not for my OCD, I&#39;d have thrown it aside by now. Please tell me it gets better? I&#39;ve just started the letters from the friend that joined the assassin monks. That was a nice break from whatever it is I&#39;d been reading in previous pages!</a>
